name: Foulgers Creek
description:
Introduction

First descent September 9th 2019. Clare Stenham-Brown, Andrew Humphreys and Michael Henson. The canyon starts in a tributary of Foulger Creek which enters Foulger from the South. Some super nice pools. Long non-vertical rappels in moderate flow.
